The National Insurance Commission (NAICOM) has approved the appointment of Japhet Duru as new executive director, Technical at Old Mutual General Insurance Company Nigeria. Duru will oversee the operations department of the organization with a view to bolster its underwriting operations and maintain its prompt claims settlement. Duru, an Economics graduate of the Imo State University started his career at Valid Insurance Limited. Prior to joining Old Mutual General Insurance, he served as the General Manager/Chief Operating Officer at HIERS Insurance Brokers Limited. Duru has also held various senior management positions such as Head of Underwriting at KBL Insurance Ltd, Group Head Technical at International Energy Insurance Ltd and Head of Operations at Stanbic IBTC Insurance Brokers Limited. Japhet Duru also holds a Masterâ€™s degree in Finance from Lagos State University and is a Fellow of the Chartered Insurance Institute of Nigeria (CIIN). 